       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
         PROGRAM-ID. CONCATENATION-PROGRAM.
         AUTHOR HAWIN.
  
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
         CONFIGURATION SECTION.
           SOURCE-COMPUTER. IBM-3278.
           OBJECT-COMPUTER. IBM-3278.
    
       DATA DIVISION.
         WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
         01 STR1 PIC A(5).
         01 STR2 PIC A(5).
         01 RESULT PIC A(10).
         01 COUNTER PIC 9(2).
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           DISPLAY "CONCATENATION-PROGRAM RUNNING...".
    
           ACCEPT STR1.
           ACCEPT STR2.
    
           STRING STR1 DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  STR2 DELIMITED BY SIZE
                  INTO RESULT
           
           END-STRING.
    
           INSPECT RESULT TALLYING COUNTER FOR CHARACTERS BEFORE SPACE.
           DISPLAY RESULT.
           DISPLAY COUNTER.
    
           STOP-RUN.
